  <chunk id="17752cd197628ca49a7b800528bdd68532e4a148.c3" text="Conclusions/Significance: Ezrin interacts with SARS-CoV S endodomain and limits virus entry and fusion. Our data present a novel mechanism involving a cellular factor in the regulation of S-dependent early events of infection."/>
